<section class="oe_container oe_dark">
    <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
        <h2 class="oe_slogan">Payroll Department Statement Wizard</h2>
        <br/>
        <p>
            By clicking this <b>Export Excel</b> button it will export department wise payroll statement for selected department. Note that department on wizard is option if you do not select department in wizard then module will print for all department in system where payslips have been generated.
If department is not available on employee form then it will group all those payslips in Unknow department and show in excel as well.
        </p>
